@startuml Submit Document Request
!theme plain
autonumber

actor Student
participant "Student Dashboard" as UI
participant "Request View" as RequestView
participant "StudentMasterList" as MasterList
participant "DocumentType" as DocumentType
participant "DocumentRequest" as Request
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

Student -> UI : Select document, delivery method, purpose
UI -> RequestView : POST submit_request
RequestView -> MasterList : Load student profile
RequestView -> DocumentType : Load selected document types

alt Restricted request with unpaid balance
  RequestView --> UI : Reject submission
else Valid request
  loop For each selected document
    RequestView -> Request : Create DocumentRequest\nstatus=PENDING
  end
  RequestView -> Notify : Queue student notice
  Notify --> RequestView : queued
  RequestView --> UI : Success message
end

@enduml
